This project generates the economic tech trees for the different tribes in the
Widelands game.

Usage:

	make DIR=/path/to/widelands dot
		--	Generate the dot files for the economic tech trees.
			This uses the conf files in the specified Widelands
			sources.

	make svgz
		--	Generate svgz images from the tech tree dot source
			files.

	make png
		--	Generate svgz images from the tech tree dot source
			files.

	make
		--	Generate svgz and png images from the tech tree dot
			source files.

	make clean
		--	Removes the generated svgz and png images files.

